reviewText: This tape is OK but just Ok. Nothing really special. Does what it says it will and is an Ok addition to a collection. The worst thing was after I bought the tape I immediately saw the same tape for $1.00 at the Salvation Army store. With shipping and handling I paid a lot more than that. So you might want to check your local thrift stores first.
I wanted to learn Country Line Dancing so I called on Amazon because I knew that I could find this info. Thanks for a great product.
